This rpath stuff is really confusing, and I can't find much helpful stuff online about it

Update, tried with a fresh wheel and this command was sufficient to solve the problem:

{code}
install_name_tool -add_rpath @loader_path/ lib.cpython-36m-darwin.so 
{code}

So it seems we only need to fix the Cython extensions

